Addendum by James Suzuki, 02/05/2025
The Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch consists of source code from
Disney Interactive's STAR WARS: EMPIRE AT WAR.  EULA and other related
user-end contracts all state that all content is owned by Disney Inter-
active, and no implication is made to the contrary.

The Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch uses The Unlicense to clarify
nothing in STAR WARS: EMPIRE AT WAR is owned by Suzuki or related con-
tributors.  All content is owned by Disney Interactive.

However, in the spirit of open-source projects, the developers and con-
tributors of the Unofficial Forces of Corruption Patch should be credited,
as they are seen in the file READ.ME, because they are the building blocks
of this project's existence.
